info.title: Terms for extending OData Metadata to accommodate RESO specific requirements
info.description:
This OData service is located at http://localhost/service-root/

## Term Definitions
Term|Description
----|----
StandardName|The standard name of the entity, property, enumeration, or enumeration value
LocalName|The localized name of the entity, property, enumeration, or enumeration value.
